channel.title: Food Isn't Working
channel.description:
How do I fix the food?
I was editing my server and compiling every so often so that I could see were the errors where and in the end I got no errors so it's all ok. Then I tried pking, I went to eat but my health didn't increase and the manta was still in my inventory.
I don't remember which parts of my server I removed.
Could someone please tell me how to get the food working again please? :)
